":"definition","text":"a.中等收入的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎middle-income group中等收入人群"},{"type":"entry","text":"by the hour 按时计算","headword":"by the hour"},{"type":"entry","text":"occupational injury 工伤，职业伤害","headword":"occupational injury"},{"type":"entry","text":"high-risk [ˌhaɪ ˈrɪsk]","headword":"high-risk"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.高风险的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎high-risk operation高风险作业"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"}]},{"number":960,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"A：Waiter, keep the food coming, please. John, keep eating!（服务"},{"type":"text","text":"生，请接着上菜。约翰，继续吃啊！）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：I've been eating for the past thirty minutes! I'm pretty much full."},{"type":"text","text":"（我已经连续吃了半小时了！我吃得太饱了。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：So you just bought the car right away?（所以你就立刻买下了那"},{"type":"text","text":"辆车？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Yeah, the salesman was a smooth talker.（是的，那个推销员是"},{"type":"text","text":"个能说会道的人。）"}]}]}